		<div class="quote"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//en.wikivoyage.org/wiki/Seminole_Wars" title="Seminole Wars">A result of American settlement in the contested forests and prairies of colonial Florida, the devastating Seminole Wars fought between U.S. forces and Seminoles in Florida left behind wartime artifacts, forts, and plantation ruins from the 19th century.</a></div>
